      },
    ],
    comment: '<p>In HTML the <code>&#x3C;select></code> element is used to create drop-down lists.\nThe available options in the <code>&#x3C;select></code> list are created with the <code>&#x3C;option></code> tag.</p>\n<p>Example:</p>\n<pre><code class="language-html">&#x3C;form>\n&#x3C;select>\n  &#x3C;option\n    value="apple">Apples\n  &#x3C;/option>\n  &#x3C;option\n   value="banana">Bananas\n  &#x3C;/option>\n  &#x3C;option\n    value="orange">Oranges\n  &#x3C;/option>\n  &#x3C;option\n    value="plum">Plums\n  &#x3C;/option>\n  &#x3C;option\n    value="lemon">Lemons\n  &#x3C;/option>\n&#x3C;/select>\n&#x3C;/form>\n</code></pre>\n<p><svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" style="width:100%" viewBox="0 0 320 146"><g fill="none" fill-rule="evenodd"><rect width="320" height="146" fill="#FFF" rx="9"/><path fill="#3B99FC" stroke="#3497FF" d="M71 37.11593V21h11.07254c1.5431 1.05927 2.31463 2.59597 2.31463 4.6101 0 1.0728.36942 9.10886-1.15003 10.46117-1.52922 1.361-5.60826 1.70921-12.23714 1.04466z"/><rect width="64" height="17" x="20.5" y="20.5" stroke="#D9D9D9" rx="4"/><text fill="#000" font-family="ArialMT, Arial" font-size="11.5"><tspan x="28" y="33">Apples </tspan></text><path stroke="#FFF" stroke-linecap="square" d="M75.375 26.625l2.25-2.25m-.25 0l2.25 2.25M75.5 30l2.25 2.25m2-2.25l-2.25 2.25"/><g transform="translate(28 34)"><text fill="#000" font-family="ArialMT, Arial" font-size="11.5"><tspan x="3" y="10">Red</tspan></text><rect width="75" height="90" x=".5" y="1.5" fill="#F9FBFB" fill-rule="nonzero" stroke="#D2D2D2" rx="4"/><text fill="#000" font-family="ArialMT, Arial" font-size="11.5"><tspan x="21" y="18">Apples</tspan></text><path fill="#479AFE" fill-rule="nonzero" d="M1 38h74v16H1z"/><text fill="#FFF" font-family="ArialMT, Arial" font-size="11.5"><tspan x="21" y="50">Oranges</tspan></text><text fill="#000" font-family="ArialMT, Arial" font-size="11.5"><tspan x="21" y="66">Plums</tspan></text><text fill="#000" font-family="ArialMT, Arial" font-size="11.5